ls></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRLayer\"><code>XRLayer</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebXR Device API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/xr\"><code>Navigator.xr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext/makeXRCompatible\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext.makeXRCompatible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRAnchor\"><code>XRAnchor</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRBoundedReferenceSpace\"><code>XRBoundedReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCPUDepthInformation\"><code>XRCPUDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRDepthInformation\"><code>XRDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRFrame\"><code>XRFrame</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSource\"><code>XRInputSource</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourceArray\"><code>XRInputSourceArray</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourceEvent\"><code>XRInputSourceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRInputSourcesChangeEvent\"><code>XRInputSourcesChangeEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRPose\"><code>XRPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpace\"><code>XRReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpaceEvent\"><code>XRReferenceSpaceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRenderState\"><code>XRRenderState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRigidTransform\"><code>XRRigidTransform</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSession\"><code>XRSession</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSessionEvent\"><code>XRSessionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSpace\"><code>XRSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSystem\"><code>XRSystem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView\"><code>XRView</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewerPose\"><code>XRViewerPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewport\"><code>XRViewport</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding\"><code>XRWebGLBinding</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLDepthInformation\"><code>XRWebGLDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLLayer\"><code>XRWebGLLayer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>chromaticAberrationCorrection</code></strong> property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer\"><code>XRCompositionLayer</code></a> interface is a boolean enabling the layer's optical chromatic aberration correction.</p>\n<p>Chromatic aberration (\"color fringing\") is an imperfection wherein a lens fails to focus all wavelengths of colors at the same point. This effect results in a seven-colored rainbow. To remove these imperfections a process called chromatic aberration correction is needed. For more information, read <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chromatic_aberration\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Chromatic aberration</a> on Wikipedia.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  A boolean. <code>true</code> enables chromatic aberration correction for the layer; <code>false</code> disables it.\n  If the device doesn't support this feature, <code>chromaticAberrationCorrection</code> is <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a> and setting it will not do anything.\n</p>\n<p>If <code>chromaticAberrationCorrection</code> was changed, it will take effect in the next frame.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"setting_a_layers_chromatic_aberration_correction","title":"Setting a layer's chromatic aberration correction","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The following code snippet enables the layer's chromatic aberration correction.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>myLayer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>chromaticAberrationCorrection <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"query":"api.XRCompositionLayer.chromaticAberrationCorrection","specifications":[]}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.XRCompositionLayer.chromaticAberrationCorrection","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chromatic_aberration\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Chromatic aberration</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The chromaticAberrationCorrection property of the XRCompositionLayer interface is a boolean enabling the layer's optical chromatic aberration correction.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:23:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xrcompositionlayer/chromaticaberrationcorrection","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/xrcompositionlayer/chromaticaberrationcorrection/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/073f70e052ff92ab715df3c20678c11c9b51747f","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer","title":"XRCompositionLayer"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRCompositionLayer/chromaticAberrationCorrection","title":"XRCompositionLayer.chromaticAberrationCorrection"}],"pageTitle":"XRCompositionLayer.chromaticAberrationCorrection - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}